    "illustrationAlt": "Flat illustration of a row of flags on poles with a magnifying glass held over two near-identical tricolors",
    "cardDescription": "Chad vs Romania, Ireland vs Côte d'Ivoire — 15 lookalike flags and the one detail that separates each pair.",
